country's pressing economic problems, convening his Cabinet only
hours after being elected. He vowed to plow ahead with reforms and
a stimulus package.
</P>
<P>
"We think it's quite important for the new Japanese government
to expeditiously implement a reform and modernization package
along the lines that we had discussed with them," McCurry said.
