projects to be agreed upon by the two sides.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, China also decided to provide a grant of 10 million
Chinese Yuan (1.2 million U.S. Dollars) to Zimbabwe.
</P>
<P>
Half of the grant will be channeled toward offsetting costs
for the valley dam in Kezi being built by China while the rest
would be used for projects to be agreed upon.
</P>
<P>
At the signing ceremony, Chinamasa said the financial
cooperation between the two countries has brought immense
benefits to the Zimbabwean people.
</P>
<P>
Sun Guangxiang hoped the areas of Sino-Zimbabwean economic
cooperation will be further widened and enter into a new level.
</P>
