condemn terrorist activities in Kosovo, and cut off all sources of
funds to the "terrorists". (Yugoslavia-EU-Kosovo)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
ANKARA -- Turkish and Greek soldiers exchanged fire during a
border incident on the banks of the Meric River, which divides the
two countries, the semi-official Anatolia News Agency reported
here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
