highlighting the north China port city of Tianjin has attracted
more than one million users.
</P>
<P>
The Tianjin Hot Line offers information for wide-ranging
areas, including tourism, financial affairs, education, libraries,
weather forecasts, labor markets, commerce, and telecommunications
services.
</P>
<P>
